Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:19.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:21.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we set out as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you become our comrade, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:26.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.  What are you asking this late in the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:28.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm obviously making up for your incompetence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:29.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget already, you trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear like toilet paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:34.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:36.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade's out there doing her best for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:37.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With this opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:40.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to find every SSS member we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:49.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:51.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:55.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're thinking we're ready to call it quits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.02,0:00:58.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We understood after hearing your speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:01:00.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We made our decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just the kind of group we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:05.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without hearing it, we kind of already understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:08.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our vocalists disappeared already, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:11.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no replacement for Iwasawa-san and Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, her singing was pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:18.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day was as exciting as the Culture Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:19.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, those outside our group might be tough to convince.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:24.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:28.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to do it, do it to completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:29.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:32.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll just look like you persuaded us for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:37.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If this Warfront that's continued for so long is to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:42.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to think this world, and you too, will have fulfilled its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:45.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll feel like it's started to become a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:48.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For us, even for a short time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:50.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the adolescence that we weren't able to experience before...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:55.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to feel that we at last had an enjoyable one...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:58.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I have no idea at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:07.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we won't know what happens from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:08.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be on our way, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:11.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:12.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,new guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:16.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll form a band next time around, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:17.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:19.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll love it again, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:20.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:26.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you saw off the commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:27.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:30.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your personality is seriously bankrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:31.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My personality isn't bankrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:34.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're saying to God!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit messing around and let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:48.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the NPCs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:51.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, it looks like these guys are all that remain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:54.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What it is we're planning to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:55.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they've realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:08.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.  Peasants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:09.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:11.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can always count on you, Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:14.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna fight for us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:21.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I only move when I can be of use to Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haha.  Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:26.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are devoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:34.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I don't have any redeeming features...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'm able to do well here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if even God will be astonished!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:42.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him what you're made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't do for you to forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:52.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like nobody would notice if I disappeared at this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.50,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,WOOHOOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:58.21,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,COME ON, COME ON, COME ON, COME ON, COME OOOON!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:02.25,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Knocking on Heaven's door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:05.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Bob Dylan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:07.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's very appropriate for this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:09.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like everyone's starting to gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:20.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:21.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More like what's going on with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:28.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was training in the mountains for a while, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:30.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there was hardly anything to eat there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Matsushita-godan!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:34.99,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Tastyyyyyy CANDY!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost a lot of weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your body alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  In fact, better than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:45.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I feel like I could take on a 100-man Kumite!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:47.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Karate, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:50.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well whatever, it's helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:52.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, these are the troops we've got to work with now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's tear it up and get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:57.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.86,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye Wild Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's break through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the perfect place to hide out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's enemy territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is supposed to be our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I should expect them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In swarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:27.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.  There's no end to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-san.  Look down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're multiplying faster than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:38.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:46.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,100 men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it as though you're now 100 men stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:49.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:55.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:01.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me, Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:04.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?  Otonashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Their numbers increasing must mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading the right way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm running low.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:16.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With those numbers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll never make it through with just a handgun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:23.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:26.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Guild has been apprised of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now all members are making for the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:35.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:42.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the fighting going to end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  It's ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:50.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case we'll be disbanding as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:57.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to come this far because you all were fighting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:01.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:02.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We never could have gotten started in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:06.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:08.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been nothing more than a lone fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:10.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:16.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:31.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I go too far?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:38.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time for a short break...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tenshi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:50.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... Kanade-chan.  I wonder if she's fighting too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:54.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what would have happened if I had understood her sooner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:59.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's possible we would have gotten along well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're fellow girls, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:03.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even in this world...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:08.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe we could have looked for clothes together and stuff.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:12.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, maybe it couldn't have happened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't forgive him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:23.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:26.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:28.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:29.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:32.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappeeear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:51.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Therefore... this formula is very important to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:47.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:51.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like I was thinking about something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:52.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm gonna erase this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:53.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:54.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Nakamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I erase it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:02.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awww damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:18.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing in the middle of class?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:21.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:23.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:25.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked to me like you were just being absent-minded...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:28.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were thinking about love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had one I'd like to think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:35.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I think Fujiwara-kun would be a good match for you, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:40.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara-kun is all alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara-kuuu{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:45.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey don't do that, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:49.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... who are you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:50.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:51.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... oh.  Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:56.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:01.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're about to say it's love again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:07.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:12.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you remember this part well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:13.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:14.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:18.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Nakamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Read the next page from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?  What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really quite peaceful, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:36.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:39.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really a peaceful scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:41.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all living in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:47.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I disappear from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:51.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can try it all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:55.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This happiness that seems so natural...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:00.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lose my memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Change my personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:13.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you call that making a fresh start?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:16.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my life anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's somebody else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:22.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we only get one life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:24.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:26.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:29.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:31.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hand it over to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:33.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be taken, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't force it on someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:37.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't erase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trample it underfoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't laugh it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:41.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't pretend it was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:42.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:43.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all just what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:45.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cruel, but irreplaceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is accept our one and only life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:51.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei... do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:56.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll continue to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:11:59.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:00.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A life like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:11.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:20.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:26.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-kun and... Hinata-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:31.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:36.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your memories just exploded, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:38.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade was worried and brought us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:40.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:44.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:51.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you guys, why are you down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We left it up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The others, they're carrying on our will for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you came to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:01.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We all fought together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:03.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the same as always?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:08.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't help but worry about you, Yurippe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:10.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, do you want to fix your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're moving out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:20.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:22.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:24.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:32.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:33.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it seem like they're protecting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why what a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:42.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... we'd need a carpet bomb to take care of all those...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:43.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:44.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:46.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she trying to kill herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, hang on a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:01.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:05.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's combat power is greater than a bomber?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:13.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:17.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, you go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take care of these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:36.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm being mocked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:39.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... this time, for sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How the heck many did he take?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no question about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done making it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to mock me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:08.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Making that ostentatious nameplate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:11.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well this is a school, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:14.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have some interesting values.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:17.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, that's simply a rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of this world's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:22.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:24.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he exist or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:26.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite a profound question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:32.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'm in no position to determine the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:35.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I merely abide by the established rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your actions have been programmed, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's precisely as you've surmised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:41.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who programmed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I give you a name, it won't make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a person from long, long, ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Player...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:51.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that software?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As you already know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:57.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a software that can create and alter the materials of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can it do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:03.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?  I'm not the developer, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:07.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you people create weapons out of earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably the same idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:14.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, we've both been exploiting the same rules.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:20.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the developer of that software trying to become God?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?  I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:25.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.  I don't have much time, so let's move to the main question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:30.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Under what circumstances is your programming activated?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the contents of the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:35.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me rephrase my question then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened in this world that made you awaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:41.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Love has begun to bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:45.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:46.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:48.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:51.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't supposed to exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:53.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:59.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we could remember love, we'd all have disappeared right away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, if that began to blossom, what would happen to this world?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:05.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If love were to blossom here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:08.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This place would become an eternal paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:11.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this world can't become such a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is a place where...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:16.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we have to eventually graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was someone who believed that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:19.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was someone who lived their life for the sake of others...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and was sent off to their final reward...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:27.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but lost their memory and came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:30.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when bugs can start to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:34.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the programmer of Angel Player?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:37.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have quite an insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:41.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person became aware of the bugs in this world, and began to amend them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone experienced the bug, Kage would turn them into an NPC.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:46.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:47.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:48.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:52.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the NPCs, there's others just like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:53.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:54.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The poor soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the programmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:00.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been waiting the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:07.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For a girl he loved, who left this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:08.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no possibility of meeting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:13.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an astronomical number,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but the odds are not zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:19.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the time spent waiting for her was too long
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:22.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and he was unable to retain his sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:26.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he created a program to turn himself into an NPC.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:30.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe he did that first...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:34.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then applied measures to ensure that such a thing would never happen again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:36.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:39.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the day come when that person is fulfilled at last?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:43.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to know what's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's right or wrong any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:50.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you, who have managed to make it this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:53.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be able to discover the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:55.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:59.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on your own will, you could be able to change this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:03.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Change it, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:06.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can choose the path he was unable to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:10.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean... I could become God?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:12.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.87,0:19:16.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I turn this world into an eternal paradise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He rejected that option, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:21.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I should say I don't possess the emotion to reject it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:26.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:29.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, this world's God?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:42.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's finally in my grasp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:43.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:45.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've finally...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:48.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reason I fought so long was all for this moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could even beat Tenshi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:52.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the power of this system...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd be the strongest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:03.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Kanade-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I came this far is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest I've ever felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's magnifying at a terrifying rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:27.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:29.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the reason why I've come this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so I can protect everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:37.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, so you're the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:40.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:43.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut down all the machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:44.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:45.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:48.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought this through?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:52.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternity, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:56.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me teach you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:20:59.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for 10 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:02.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just stay still and do nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:41.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:43.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it over?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:45.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone is safe now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:49.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they must have safely...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:52.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Made it out of this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:56.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a blunder.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as much as you three.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:03.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came to see everyone as just as precious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:07.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I wanted to make you all proud...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:10.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By being a sister that would always love only you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:15.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah... what is this feeling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.37,0:22:17.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's happened to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:21.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the things that were driving me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:22.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're disappearing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:25.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If they disappear...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:27.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't be able to stay in this world any more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:29.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though life is so unfair.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.92,0:22:33.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though you were stolen away from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:34.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.64,0:22:36.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time I spent with everyone was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:38.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Irreplaceable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:40.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:44.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Want to try to catch up with everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:49.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:51.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:54.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be the only one suffering anymore, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:58.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard for a long time, Onee-chan.
