Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:24.38,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,340)}When I turned around, everyone was far away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:32.06,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Even so, I walked on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:37.69,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,400)}That's what it was to be strong
