Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:12.89,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll continue to live only through their memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:20.69,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs50}Rather than try to love and laugh at this loneliness
